Privacy Policy for "Eggcellent Adventure" game

Last updated: 02.04.2023

This Privacy Policy describes the information practices of "Eggcellent Adventure," a mobile game developed and published by Yenko Games. By using "Eggcellent Adventure," you agree to the collection and use of your information in accordance with this policy.

Information Collection and Use

"Eggcellent Adventure" does not collect any personally identifiable information from its users. The app is designed to operate without requiring any personal data from users.

Offline User Score

"Eggcellent Adventure" stores user scores locally on the device. This information is not shared with any third parties and is not transmitted over the Internet.

Third-Party Integrations

"Eggcellent Adventure" does not include any third-party integrations, such as analytics, crash reporting tools, or ad services that might collect user data.

Social Media

The app does not offer social media integration or sharing features, ensuring no user data is shared with social media platforms.

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to update or change our Privacy Policy at any time. You should check this Privacy Policy periodically for updates. Your continued use of "Eggcellent Adventure" after we post any modifications to the Privacy Policy on this page will constitute your acknowledgment of the modifications and your consent to abide and be bound by the modified Privacy Policy.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at eggcellent.adventure@proton.me.
